msgid ""
msgstr ""
"Project-Id-Version: Yakuza 6 Translation\n"
"Last-Translator: SavT\n"
"MIME-Version: 1.0\n"
"Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8\n"
"Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit\n"
"Language: it\n"

msgctxt "0||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san! Sorry to keep you waiting. <symbol=note_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1||||4"
msgid "Sorry! Did I make you wait?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san! I'm excited to see you again. <symbol=note_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3||||4"
msgid "So, where should we go?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4||||4"
msgid "Karaoke, huh? Sounds good! <symbol=note_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5||||4"
msgid "I don't normally play darts, but I'm excited!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||||4"
msgid "Okay, let's go! <symbol=note_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "7||||4"
msgid "I wonder what you'll sing... <symbol=heart_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "8||||4"
msgid "What should I sing today? <symbol=note_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "9||||4"
msgid "I'm not so good, so go easy on me! <symbol=heart_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "10||||4"
msgid "Okay, here I go!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "11||||4"
msgid "Let's just focus on enjoying the rest, okay? <symbol=note_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "12||||4"
msgid "That was fun! We should come back soon. <symbol=note_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "13||||4"
msgid "That was so fun! <symbol=heart_with_outline>\r\nWe should definitely do this again sometime. <symbol=note_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14||||4"
msgid "Shall we head back to the club?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "15||||4"
msgid "This one's my specialty. <symbol=note_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "16||||4"
msgid "Oh, maybe I'll sing this one. <symbol=note_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17||||4"
msgid "Hmm... I guess that song was too hard."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "18||||4"
msgid "It was kinda hard to sing..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "19||||4"
msgid "It was really fun to sing with you. <symbol=note_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "20||||4"
msgid "That song felt really good!\r\nYou're great at keeping the mood up! <symbol=note_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "21||||4"
msgid "I want to hear you sing something, too. <symbol=note_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "22||||4"
msgid "Aww... There's no need to be shy..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "23||||4"
msgid "Oh... Uh... That was good...!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "24||||4"
msgid "You're so good, Kiryu-san. <symbol=note_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||||4"
msgid "You sing incredibly well. <symbol=note_with_outline> I could listen\r\nto you sing like that for hours on end. <symbol=heart_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "26||||4"
msgid "Whoa! You've got deep pockets!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "27||||4"
msgid "Thank you very much!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||||4"
msgid "Huh...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "29||||4"
msgid "Oh, I like that one, too. <symbol=note_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "30||||4"
msgid "Thank you for waiting."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "31||||4"
msgid "It's a pleasure to meet you. I'm Hikaru."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "32||||4"
msgid "Um, and your name is?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "33||||4"
msgid "Oh. I'm Kiryu."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "34||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san? Well then, I look forward to spending some\r\ntime with you, Kiryu-san!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "35||||4"
msgid "Yeah, same here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "36||||4"
msgid "Thank you for coming in today, Kiryu-san.\r\nI enjoyed all the different topics! <symbol=note_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "37||||4"
msgid "Come back soon, won't you? <symbol=heart_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "38||||4"
msgid "Yeah, I'll be back."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "39||||4"
msgid "And I'll be waiting. <symbol=heart_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "40||||4"
msgid "Thanks for visiting me again, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "41||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san, welcome back.\r\nI've been waiting for you. <symbol=heart_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "42||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san, welcome back.\r\nI was hoping you'd come back again... <symbol=heart_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "43||||4"
msgid "I'd like to spend more time\r\nwith you today. <symbol=heart_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "44||||4"
msgid "Right this way."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||||4"
msgid "Thank you for coming today. <symbol=note_with_outline>\r\nI'll be waiting for your next visit."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "47||||4"
msgid "Thank you for coming today. <symbol=note_with_outline>\r\nCome back soon. <symbol=heart_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "48||||4"
msgid "Thank you for coming today. <symbol=note_with_outline>\r\nI hope to see you again soon... <symbol=heart_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "49||||4"
msgid "Let's have some fun today. <symbol=heart_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||||4"
msgid "Cheers! <symbol=note_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "51||||4"
msgid "Um, Kiryu-san!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "52||||4"
msgid "Here, you can have my phone number.\r\nCall me anytime you want, okay? <symbol=heart_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "53||||4"
msgid "It looks like our time's up."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "54||||4"
msgid "We're out of time,\r\nbut I'd love to talk more..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "55||||4"
msgid "I'm so happy! <symbol=note_with_outline>\r\nYou're the best, Kiryu-san. <symbol=heart_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "56||||4"
msgid "Thank you so much for today! <symbol=note_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||||4"
msgid "Okay, got it! <symbol=note_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "58||||4"
msgid "Hmm, okay..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "59||||4"
msgid "Yeah!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||||4"
msgid "If you don't mind... <symbol=heart_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||||4"
msgid "No way."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||||4"
msgid "That's not right at all!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||||4"
msgid "What? You think so?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||||4"
msgid "I'll pass. <symbol=note_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||||4"
msgid "Wow, really?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||||4"
msgid "See you later!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "67||||4"
msgid "Oh, Kiryu-san. <symbol=heart_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "68||||4"
msgid "That's top secret. <symbol=note_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "69||||4"
msgid "Um... Did you have fun talking\r\nwith me today, Kiryu-san?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "70||||4"
msgid "What? Where's this coming from?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "71||||4"
msgid "My customers are always telling me\r\nI'm too quiet, or that I have no energy."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "72||||4"
msgid "Oh. Well, you do seem pretty calm."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "73||||4"
msgid "Lately, I've been wondering if a hostess\r\nneeds to be more upbeat and energetic."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "74||||4"
msgid "I mean, the girls like that get more customers,\r\nand they bring in more profit for the club."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "75||||4"
msgid "That's what you're worried about?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "76||||4"
msgid "Then, why don't we practice being energetic?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "77||||4"
msgid "Huh? Practice?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "78||||4"
msgid "Yeah, if you want to become your ideal self,\r\nyou have to put in the effort first."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "79||||4"
msgid "You've gotta face the challenge head on, with\r\nthe knowledge that you can become better."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "80||||4"
msgid "I see... I think you're right.\r\nYou mind if we give it a shot?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "81||||4"
msgid "No prob."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "82||||4"
msgid "Yaaaaay!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "83||||4"
msgid "Hmmm..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "84||||4"
msgid "Yahoo!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "85||||4"
msgid "Nice..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "86||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san... I just can't do it... Wait,\r\ndid you trick me into this to tease me?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "87||||4"
msgid "You got me..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "88||||4"
msgid "Oh come on, Kiryu-san!\r\nAt least try to help me out!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "89||||4"
msgid "Sorry, sorry. But it got you to be a\r\nlittle more energetic, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "90||||4"
msgid "You're right... Shoot.\r\nYou're better than I thought."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "91||||4"
msgid "Well, you're fun to be with just as you\r\nare. I don't think you need to force it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "92||||4"
msgid "Thank you. You're right.\r\nI'll try to work on it in my own way."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "93||||4"
msgid "Hikaru, I think you're fine as you are."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "95||||4"
msgid "Not everyone comes to a cabaret club\r\nexpecting a wild party with energetic girls."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "96||||4"
msgid "Some guys just want to have a drink with a\r\ngirl like you in a place they can relax."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "97||||4"
msgid "Kind of like... me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "98||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||||4"
msgid "So, stay just the way you are."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "100||||4"
msgid "There's nothing so wrong with you that you'd\r\nneed to hide who you really are, you know?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "101||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san... <symbol=heart_with_outline> Thank you so much.\r\nI'm feeling really optimistic all of a sudden."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "102||||4"
msgid "I'll work hard in my own, relaxed way. I hope\r\nyou'll keep coming to take it easy with me. <symbol=heart_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "103||||4"
msgid "Yeah, of course."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "104||||4"
msgid "If you're worried about something as silly as that,\r\nhow about I spend all my money to make you number one?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||||4"
msgid "Huh!? Oh no, I could never. Please don't\r\nwaste your money on something like that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "106||||4"
msgid "But... then you'd be number one, yeah?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "107||||4"
msgid "But... that doesn't feel right.\r\nI want to aim for the top in my own way."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "108||||4"
msgid "I thought you might say that.\r\nLooks like you already have your answer."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "109||||4"
msgid "Oh..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "110||||4"
msgid "I think you've gotta be yourself, Hikaru.\r\nI like that, and that's why I requested you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "111||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san... Thank you. You're right.\r\nI shouldn't push myself too hard."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "112||||4"
msgid "I'll work hard in my own, relaxed way! I hope\r\nyou'll come back and help me see it through."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "113||||4"
msgid "Yeah. Give it your best shot."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "114||||4"
msgid "Just curious, but, why'd you\r\ndecide to become a hostess?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||||4"
msgid "I'm a student, so... I need to pay my tuition.\r\nI'm paying my own way through school."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "116||||4"
msgid "That's admirable."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "117||||4"
msgid "Oh, not at all. I'm about to graduate,\r\nso I really oughta be looking for a real job..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "118||||4"
msgid "So, have you been?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "119||||4"
msgid "No, actually... I have a dream...\r\nI want to become an idol."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "120||||4"
msgid "An idol?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "121||||4"
msgid "Yeah... I've been looking into it a little\r\nhere and there, but it's not going anywhere..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "122||||4"
msgid "I'm already 23... I should probably give\r\nup on that and look for a real job, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "123||||4"
msgid "I'm behind you all the way.\r\nYou shouldn't give up on your dreams."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "124||||4"
msgid "Really?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "125||||4"
msgid "Yeah. You only live once, so you've\r\ngotta make your time count."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "126||||4"
msgid "But, if you don't fully commit to it, you may\r\nactually regret not giving up when you could have."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "127||||4"
msgid "So... decide whether or not you're serious about\r\nthis, and make the call. If you are, I'm behind you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "128||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san... Thank you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "129||||4"
msgid "Your words hit me really hard... Maybe I was\r\nnaive for even worrying over it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "130||||4"
msgid "I'll have to dig deep and give it some real thought.\r\nIf I do decide to go for it... I hope you'll root for me!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "131||||4"
msgid "Of course. I'll be your first fan."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "132||||4"
msgid "Yaaay! <symbol=heart_with_outline> I'll work hard at it!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "133||||4"
msgid "Shouldn't you at least be looking?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "134||||4"
msgid "So you think so too, huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "135||||4"
msgid "Yeah. But I only feel that way because\r\nI can tell you're being indecisive."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "136||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||||4"
msgid "If you really want to make a dream come true,\r\nyou have to be determined to see it happen."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "138||||4"
msgid "If you're hesitating now, then you may as well\r\ngive it up. Being an idol is no walk in the park."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "139||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "140||||4"
msgid "But, if one day you can say from the bottom of\r\nyour heart that you want to be an idol, I'm behind you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||||4"
msgid "Everyone looks up to idols, and idols have to\r\nshoulder those dreams. It's no walk in the park."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "143||||4"
msgid "I actually know a former idol, and society and the\r\nmedia can be both a blessing and a curse."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "144||||4"
msgid "If you mess up, everything can come crashing down\r\nin an instant. It's that strict, and you have to be strong."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "145||||4"
msgid "So, I can't just casually say, yeah, go for it,\r\nyou have my support."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "146||||4"
msgid "......"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "147||||4"
msgid "But, it's also the kind of job where your hard work and\r\ndetermination pay off by giving people courage and smiles."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "148||||4"
msgid "If you're ready to bear that burden...\r\nThen I'm behind you all the way."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "149||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san... Thank you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "150||||4"
msgid "You're actually the first person who's taken it\r\nthat seriously and been honest about it. I'm so happy."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "151||||4"
msgid "I... may have been a little naive. You can't aim\r\nfor something this hard half-heartedly."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "152||||4"
msgid "I think I need to take a long, hard look in the mirror."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "153||||4"
msgid "Yeah."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "154||||4"
msgid "And I hope that one day I'll be able to tell you\r\nthat I want to become an idol with pride."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "155||||4"
msgid "When you do, I'll be your first fan."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "156||||4"
msgid "Okay! <symbol=heart_with_outline> I'll work so hard, you won't be able\r\nto take your eyes off me!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "157||||4"
msgid "So? Did you end up figuring out if you want\r\nto look for a job or get into the idol thing?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "158||||4"
msgid "Yes. I was actually thinking about\r\nhow I'd tell you that today."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "159||||4"
msgid "I, Hikaru Shiota, hereby declare that\r\nI'm going to try to become a top idol!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "160||||4"
msgid "I thought you might."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "161||||4"
msgid "Yeah! And if I don't seem serious,\r\nI'm telling you, I'm quite serious!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "162||||4"
msgid "And it's all thanks to your encouragement,\r\nKiryu-san. Thank you!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "163||||4"
msgid "Hey, I just say whatever pops into my head.\r\nGood luck with it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "164||||4"
msgid "Thanks! Though I still need to consider which\r\nof my traits I want to emphasize."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "165||||4"
msgid "Traits?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "166||||4"
msgid "Yeah. Sorta like a catchphrase. If you don't set\r\nyourself apart, you'll get lost in the crowd."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "167||||4"
msgid "It's a competitive society we live in..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "168||||4"
msgid "Yeah... So, Kiryu-san, do you have any\r\nsuggestions for a catchphrase that would fit me?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "169||||4"
msgid "A catchphrase, huh... Let's see..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "170||||4"
msgid "How about, \"Check out my fine butt!\""
msgstr ""

msgctxt "171||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san... You really get how this works!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "172||||4"
msgid "I can't deny that my butt is part of my charm.\r\nIt might not be a bad idea to play that up!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "173||||4"
msgid "That said, I'm impressed that you noticed.\r\nThat means you're staring at my butt a lot, huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "174||||4"
msgid "No, all it took was a single glance..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "175||||4"
msgid "Ohhhh, you. It's written all over your face.\r\nYou're cute when you're embarrassed."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "176||||4"
msgid "How about, \"I'm such a bright, energetic, and\r\nsunny girl, that you'll need shades!\""
msgstr ""

msgctxt "177||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san, you're pretty good at this...\r\nThat does sound like a catchphrase."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "178||||4"
msgid "But I don't think I'm all that bright or\r\nenergetic, so, do you think that'll work?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "179||||4"
msgid "Don't underestimate the power of words. If you\r\nsay you're bright and energetic, they'll believe it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "180||||4"
msgid "I see. So it's kind of like getting out in front of\r\nmy shortcomings? Amazing! You're like my producer."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "181||||4"
msgid "It might work. Just keep it in mind."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "182||||4"
msgid "Okay. <symbol=note_with_outline> Thank you, Producer Kiryu. <symbol=note_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "183||||4"
msgid "How about \"Make way for the Princess of the\r\nHealer Kingdom!\""
msgstr ""

msgctxt "184||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san, you're so good at this!\r\nI appreciate the serious thought."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "185||||4"
msgid "Well, I think your softness is what makes\r\nyou so unique."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "186||||4"
msgid "I only came up with it because I think a lot of guys\r\nlike me would be drawn to the promise of healing."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "187||||4"
msgid "I'm happy you think of me that way."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "188||||4"
msgid "And you even called me a princess... <symbol=note_with_outline>\r\nYou'll make me blush."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "189||||4"
msgid "Just food for thought.\r\nI hope you'll find the right approach."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "190||||4"
msgid "Me too! <symbol=note_with_outline>\r\nThank you for your input, Producer Kiryu. <symbol=note_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "191||||4"
msgid "You know, until now, my only joy in life\r\nwas my daily dose of dried sweet potatoes..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "192||||4"
msgid "But I've discovered that talking to you is\r\nsomething I've started looking forward to!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "193||||4"
msgid "So I'm on the same level\r\nas dried sweet potatoes?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "194||||4"
msgid "Don't take it so negatively!\r\nI really, <font_kind=yakuza_italic>really</font_kind> like dried sweet potatoes."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "195||||4"
msgid "So being on that level means I <font_kind=yakuza_italic>really</font_kind>\r\nlike you too, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "196||||4"
msgid "Oh, what am I saying!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "197||||4"
msgid "Anyway, I just wanted to say it's been fun\r\ntalking to you... It makes my heart race."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "198||||4"
msgid "Your heart races, huh? That sounds...\r\n...like you might be a little love sick."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "199||||4"
msgid "Huh!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "200||||4"
msgid "Just messing with you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "201||||4"
msgid "Come on, don't tease me.\r\nBesides... I'm not joking."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "202||||4"
msgid "Hm? About what?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "203||||4"
msgid "It's nothing! Kiryu-san...\r\nYou're so dense."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "204||||4"
msgid "Am I?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "205||||4"
msgid "Yeah, well... that's actually part of your\r\ncharm, I suppose."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "206||||4"
msgid "Hm... I'll take that as a compliment."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "207||||4"
msgid "What a coincidence. Me too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "208||||4"
msgid "Huh!? Does that mean...\r\nYou feel the love too?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "209||||4"
msgid "Yeah. I feel the same way."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "210||||4"
msgid "Oh no... What should I do?\r\nI'm not ready... and you're so bold..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "211||||4"
msgid "But... I'm happy, Kiryu-san...\r\nAs long as it's with you, I..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "212||||4"
msgid "Hm? Where are you going with this?\r\nWe're talking about dried sweet potatoes, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "213||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "214||||4"
msgid "I love dried sweet potatoes, too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "215||||4"
msgid "Oh, Kiryu-san! Don't be so vague when\r\nyou say such important things!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "216||||4"
msgid "...Vague?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "217||||4"
msgid "...That's enough of that.\r\nI got all worked up for nothing."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "218||||4"
msgid "You're weird, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "219||||4"
msgid "You need to lay off the dried sweet potatoes."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "220||||4"
msgid "Huh? You think so?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "221||||4"
msgid "You know... starch goes right to the stomach."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "222||||4"
msgid "Besides, everything in moderation, you know?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "223||||4"
msgid "Okay. You're weird, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "224||||4"
msgid "Am I?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "225||||4"
msgid "Yes. Of course, I mean that in a good way."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "226||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san, I actually have something\r\nI want to report!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "227||||4"
msgid "Oh yeah? What's the occasion?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "228||||4"
msgid "I'm... going to sign a contract with a talent\r\nagency to become an idol!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "229||||4"
msgid "What? Really?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "230||||4"
msgid "Yeah! I auditioned, made it through the test,\r\nand managed to get a call back!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "231||||4"
msgid "That's great! You're an idol now!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "232||||4"
msgid "Well, this is only where it starts.\r\nThe real challenge is what comes next."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "233||||4"
msgid "But... it's all thanks to you, Kiryu-san.\r\nThank you so much!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "234||||4"
msgid "I didn't do anything.\r\nIt was all you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "235||||4"
msgid "No, this only happened because of\r\nwhat you said to me that one time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "236||||4"
msgid "I was afraid to commit to it, but you made me\r\ncome out of my shell and get serious about it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "237||||4"
msgid "You do seem more confident than back then.\r\nGive it your best shot, okay?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "238||||4"
msgid "I will! I actually have a meeting with the\r\nagency after this."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "239||||4"
msgid "The interview was held at a different location, so\r\nthis'll be my first time going to the office. I'm nervous..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "240||||4"
msgid "That's okay. There's a lot of different types of people\r\nin the entertainment industry, so just be careful, okay?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "241||||4"
msgid "I will. Thank you. <symbol=note_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "242||||4"
msgid "Well, see you later, Kiryu-san. <symbol=note_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "243||||4"
msgid "Yeah."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "244||||4"
msgid "Let's see... I like tea,\r\nso I go to a lot of tea parties."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "245||||4"
msgid "Yeah? Do you make your own tea?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "246||||4"
msgid "Yes! Of course, I like drinking it, too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "247||||4"
msgid "Oh! Would you like me to make some\r\nfor you too, Kiryu-san?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "248||||4"
msgid "Sure. Looking forward to it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "249||||4"
msgid "Hmm... I usually go shopping,\r\nor I'll just wander around outside."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "250||||4"
msgid "I see.\r\nWhat kind of stuff do you shop for?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "251||||4"
msgid "Oh, just the usual women's stuff.\r\nBeauty products, cute clothes, you know."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "252||||4"
msgid "Let me buy next time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "253||||4"
msgid "Wow, really!?\r\nThat makes me happy! <symbol=note_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "254||||4"
msgid "Buy some for me next time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "255||||4"
msgid "Huh...? Beauty products and cute clothes?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "256||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san... Are you into that kind of thing?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "257||||4"
msgid "What? N-No, it's not like that..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "258||||4"
msgid "Don't worry. I won't tell anyone!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "259||||4"
msgid "Besides, I bet you'd be pretty cute\r\nin drag, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "260||||4"
msgid "(That came out the wrong way...)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "261||||4"
msgid "Hmmm."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "262||||4"
msgid "Oh... Am I boring you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "263||||4"
msgid "No, I didn't mean that..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "264||||4"
msgid "Come on, Kiryu-san! What am I supposed\r\nto think with a response like that? Hmph!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "265||||4"
msgid "I started here just after I started college,\r\nso this'll be my fourth year."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "266||||4"
msgid "Four years, huh?\r\nWould you say you're used to the job, then?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "267||||4"
msgid "No way! I've got a ways to go. The moment I let my\r\nguard down I make mistakes, so I try to stay focused."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "268||||4"
msgid "I see. I suppose giving it that\r\nkind of attention is a good thing."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "269||||4"
msgid "I'm from Kanagawa, near the sea."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "270||||4"
msgid "Huh. So, can you swim?\r\nPeople are into surfing there, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "271||||4"
msgid "I can't swim at all... Can you, Kiryu-san?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "272||||4"
msgid "I suppose so.\r\nI've gotten into spearfishing lately."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "273||||4"
msgid "Oh, that's amazing! Woooow!\r\nYou'll have to teach me that some time!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "274||||4"
msgid "Dried sweet potatoes and beef jerky!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "275||||4"
msgid "They're kinda tough, and I like how the more\r\nyou chew them, the more flavor you get."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "276||||4"
msgid "Wow. You've got quite a refined palate."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "277||||4"
msgid "Why, thank you. <symbol=note_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "278||||4"
msgid "I suppose I like a kind man."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "279||||4"
msgid "The kind of guy who helps an old woman\r\ncarry something heavy comes to mind."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "280||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san, are you the type to help an\r\nold lady out?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "281||||4"
msgid "Isn't it obvious?\r\nOf course I would."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "282||||4"
msgid "I knew you were kind.\r\nThat's wonderful. <symbol=note_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "283||||4"
msgid "Nope, can't say I'd carry her stuff."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "284||||4"
msgid "Huh? Why not?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "285||||4"
msgid "These days, old people get mad if you\r\ntry to treat them like senior citizens."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "286||||4"
msgid "Oh, I have heard of that happening.\r\nHmmm... Must be tough."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "287||||4"
msgid "Actually, I'd pick up both the stuff\r\nand the old lady."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "288||||4"
msgid "What!? You'd carry them both!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "289||||4"
msgid "I never thought of that!\r\nYou're so kind! That's wonderful... <symbol=heart_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "290||||4"
msgid "I don't know if I'd call it kind, but..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "291||||4"
msgid "I don't think I'm all that different, but\r\nI guess I'm the type who craves attention."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "292||||4"
msgid "Oho. Attention does it for you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "293||||4"
msgid "Yep. I may-eow even talk like a cat."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "294||||4"
msgid "I'll give you as much attention as you want."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "295||||4"
msgid "Oh, Kiryu-san! <symbol=note_with_outline> I'm so happy right meow. <symbol=note_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "296||||4"
msgid "I don't really like women who beg for attention."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "297||||4"
msgid "Whaaat? You don't like me, Kiryu-san?\r\nMeow I'm all sad... <symbol=note_with_outline> I apawlogize... <symbol=note_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "298||||4"
msgid "I forgive you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "299||||4"
msgid "That's cute-meow..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "300||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san!? Did you just say \"that's cute-meow\"?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "301||||4"
msgid "N-Nope, forget I said anything."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "302||||4"
msgid "I know what I heard!\r\nYou're so mischievous that it's cute. <symbol=heart_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "303||||4"
msgid "For a long time, I've dreamt of becoming an idol."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "304||||4"
msgid "But I'm not a teenager anymore, and people tell\r\nme to just get a job... I'm keeping my options open."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "305||||4"
msgid "When I was a kid,\r\nI thought I wanted to be a teacher."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "306||||4"
msgid "A teacher, huh? That's a nice dream.\r\nWhat changed your mind?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "307||||4"
msgid "Back in school, I started hearing about\r\nthese \"monster parents.\""
msgstr ""

msgctxt "308||||4"
msgid "I figured I didn't stand a chance against\r\nany monsters, so..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "309||||4"
msgid "Monster parents...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "310||||4"
msgid "Oh, those!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "311||||4"
msgid "Exactly. It'd be tough to deal with them,\r\nyou know?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "312||||4"
msgid "Yep. Probably real difficult."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "313||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san... Are you even following?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "314||||4"
msgid "Yeah, the unreasonable types, right? The kind that\r\ncomplain about their kids' teachers to the school..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "315||||4"
msgid "Yeah. It's hard for me to be firm with people,\r\nso I'd probably have gotten sick with stress..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "316||||4"
msgid "Teachers have it rough these days...\r\nThough, I bet the kids would all like your class."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "317||||4"
msgid "You really think so? I'm happy to hear that. <symbol=note_with_outline>\r\nI love kids."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "318||||4"
msgid "Oh, someone like Kazama-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "319||||4"
msgid "Huh? Kazama-san?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "320||||4"
msgid "Yeah. He was pretty scary when he got mad.\r\nHe was kind of a monster in the underworld."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "321||||4"
msgid "Underworld? Kiryu-san, you're losing me here..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "322||||4"
msgid "Oh, I'm good at giving shoulder massages.\r\nMy friends are always telling me that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "323||||4"
msgid "I massaged my dad's shoulders a lot when I was\r\nlittle. Does Papa Kiryu want a massage, too?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "324||||4"
msgid "Oh, you don't mind?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "325||||4"
msgid "Not at all! It'll cost you extra, though. <symbol=note_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "326||||4"
msgid "Tch... You're pretty devious."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "327||||4"
msgid "I don't know if this counts as interesting,\r\nbut I did some volunteering overseas last month."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "328||||4"
msgid "Huh. Never guessed you'd be into that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "329||||4"
msgid "I am. I was helping out with some tree planting,\r\nbut physical labor is hard work."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "330||||4"
msgid "But in my free time I got to interact with the\r\nlocals, and it was a new and really fun experience."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "331||||4"
msgid "I bet. What country were you in?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "332||||4"
msgid "Myanmar."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "333||||4"
msgid "(Myanmar...?)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "334||||4"
msgid "Oh, isn't that in southeast Asia?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "335||||4"
msgid "Yeah! I'm impressed you knew that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "336||||4"
msgid "Of course. Common knowledge, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "337||||4"
msgid "Anyway, I think it's great that you're getting\r\nthat kind of experience while you're young."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "338||||4"
msgid "Thank you. I hope it ends up being useful\r\nsomehow."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "339||||4"
msgid "The place with those famous hot springs\r\nin Kusatsu?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "340||||4"
msgid "That's Gunma."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "341||||4"
msgid "Isn't that some English word for a tool?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "342||||4"
msgid "That's a \"hammer.\""
msgstr ""

msgctxt "343||||4"
msgid "Not really, but I feel like that's okay.\r\nMy philosophy is to have a few good friends."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "344||||4"
msgid "Did you know you can play games on your\r\nphone these days? I do that a lot lately."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "345||||4"
msgid "What kind of games do you play, Kiryu-san?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "346||||4"
msgid "I hit up the arcades a lot.\r\nSo, arcade games."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "347||||4"
msgid "Wow! I haven't been to one in a while.\r\nYou should take me there sometime!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "348||||4"
msgid "I'm all about the mobile games."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "349||||4"
msgid "Really? Which ones do you play?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "350||||4"
msgid "Huh? Uh, I don't know...\r\nWhatever's popular."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "351||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san... You don't really play, do you?\r\nYou need to learn how to lie better."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "352||||4"
msgid "You got me... Sorry."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "353||||4"
msgid "Lately... I'm caught up in the game of love."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "354||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san, you try to act so cool sometimes.\r\nYou're a funny guy."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "355||||4"
msgid "Huh? What secret?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "356||||4"
msgid "Well, actually..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "357||||4"
msgid "I've been to prison before."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "358||||4"
msgid "Huh? Really?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "359||||4"
msgid "But you don't seem like a bad person\r\nto me, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "360||||4"
msgid "Ah, maybe it was a false charge?\r\nOr were you trying to protect someone else?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "361||||4"
msgid "Sometimes I wonder."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "362||||4"
msgid "Well, people have all kinds of circumstances.\r\nI don't believe you're a bad person at all."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "363||||4"
msgid "People pick fights with me a lot."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "364||||4"
msgid "I bet... You kind of look like the type!\r\nI don't think that's much of a secret, really."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "365||||4"
msgid "I'm 100,024 years old."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "366||||4"
msgid "Realllllly..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "367||||4"
msgid "...Never mind."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "368||||4"
msgid "A lot of people in other countries seem to have\r\nthem. I don't think they're all that bad, really."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "369||||4"
msgid "It seems like such a painful process though...\r\nWait... Do you have one, Kiryu-san?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "370||||4"
msgid "Yeah, on my back."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "371||||4"
msgid "Wow, really?\r\nWhat kind of design is it?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "372||||4"
msgid "A dragon."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "373||||4"
msgid "Oooh, sounds cool.\r\nI kind of wanna see it..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "374||||4"
msgid "Angel wings."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "375||||4"
msgid "Aww. I hope you use those wings to fly\r\nto the future!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "376||||4"
msgid "Hikaru... It's you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "377||||4"
msgid "Huh? Me!? Did you make sure\r\nI turned out cute?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "378||||4"
msgid "Yeah, it's really cute... for a dragon."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "379||||4"
msgid "What, so it's a dragon!?\r\nYou're silly, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "380||||4"
msgid "I do drink, and I think I can hold\r\nit pretty well, too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "381||||4"
msgid "But I'm not a big fan of carbonation,\r\nso I stay away from beers and sours."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "382||||4"
msgid "But around you, who knows? I might\r\nlet my guard down and get drunk... <symbol=heart_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "383||||4"
msgid "Oh, I've heard of them. There's a lot of\r\nnaughty guys in there, aren't there?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "384||||4"
msgid "Hmm... Well, you're not wrong..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "385||||4"
msgid "Something new probably happens\r\nevery day there. Might be fun."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "386||||4"
msgid "Oh, that idol that was popular a little\r\nwhile back? She was soooo cute."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "387||||4"
msgid "I was really disappointed when she retired.\r\nWere you a fan of hers, Kiryu-san?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "388||||4"
msgid "Well... you could say that.\r\nI'm a pretty big fan."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "389||||4"
msgid "Wow, I never would've guessed!\r\nI practically had her CD on repeat."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "390||||4"
msgid "Oh! I'd love to hear about your adventures!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "391||||4"
msgid "I have kind of a legendary saga in crime."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "392||||4"
msgid "Say what?\r\nYou have legendary sugar sometimes?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "393||||4"
msgid "That's really sweet!\r\nI love brown sugar, myself. <symbol=note_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "394||||4"
msgid "A long time ago,\r\nI defeated some tigers with my bare hands."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "395||||4"
msgid "That's a good one."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "396||||4"
msgid "I cook a lot, actually. I like dried sweet potatoes,\r\nso I'm experimenting with them in my dishes."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "397||||4"
msgid "Dried sweet potatoes?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "398||||4"
msgid "Yep. Once I get it down,\r\nI'll bring you some, okay?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "399||||4"
msgid "S-Sure..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "400||||4"
msgid "I'm type A. What about you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "401||||4"
msgid "I'm type O."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "402||||4"
msgid "Really? A and O are supposed to be pretty\r\ncompatible, you know. <symbol=note_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "403||||4"
msgid "Gross, you can't just jump into dirty topics\r\nlike that... I'm not telling!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "404||||4"
msgid "What? You really want to know that much?\r\nWell... I can make an exception just for you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "405||||4"
msgid "Okay..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "406||||4"
msgid "It's actually... zero."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "407||||4"
msgid "You're lying..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "408||||4"
msgid "It's not a lie... <symbol=note_with_outline>\r\nIdols don't do stuff like that. <symbol=note_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "409||||4"
msgid "That's pretty cool..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "410||||4"
msgid "Oh... You're into that, Kiryu-san?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "411||||4"
msgid "Then I'll volunteer to be the first...\r\nKidding, of course."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "412||||4"
msgid "Oh, Kiryu-san. I hope you stay in the running. <symbol=heart_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "413||||4"
msgid "No boyfriend here! Right now I'm focused\r\non my job and my dream."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "414||||4"
msgid "Can't say that I do."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "415||||4"
msgid "Aren't you lonely?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "416||||4"
msgid "When I'm lonely, I just think about you,\r\nKiryu-san. <symbol=heart_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "417||||4"
msgid "You know how to make me happy."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "418||||4"
msgid "My dream is to become an idol, so I figured\r\nthis might give me some good experience."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "419||||4"
msgid "Huh. I guess idols and hostesses do have sort\r\nof similar traits, like..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "420||||4"
msgid "Needing communication skills?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "421||||4"
msgid "Oh, I'm impressed that you see that.\r\nThat's right! <symbol=note_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "422||||4"
msgid "These days, an idol has to do a lot more\r\nthan just be a good singer."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "423||||4"
msgid "I figured I could put some polish on my\r\ncommunication skills as a hostess."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "424||||4"
msgid "That does seem like it would be good\r\nexperience. Best of luck to you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "425||||4"
msgid "Yep! Thank you!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "426||||4"
msgid "Guys fawning over you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "427||||4"
msgid "Not at all! I meant both jobs rely pretty\r\nheavily on communication skills."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "428||||4"
msgid "Oh, right."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "429||||4"
msgid "Although, being fawned over isn't so bad,\r\neither... <symbol=note_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "430||||4"
msgid "Being able to sleep your way to the top?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "431||||4"
msgid "What? Why would you say that? That's not it at all.\r\nI meant both jobs need strong communication skills."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "432||||4"
msgid "And, you can't just sleep with people to get ahead,\r\nokay? At least, I don't!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "433||||4"
msgid "Oh, good idea.\r\nI'll be the princess, then!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "434||||4"
msgid "Uh, do you even know what the king game is?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "435||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san, don't get all high and mighty on me!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "436||||4"
msgid "I listen to a lot of rock, but I like lots of other stuff.\r\nI go to music festivals sometimes, too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "437||||4"
msgid "Yeah! I'm having fun, too. <symbol=note_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "438||||4"
msgid "I know, right? I don't really like the winter...\r\nI just want spring to last aaaaall year."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "439||||4"
msgid "Really? I get the warm and fuzzies when\r\nyou're around, Kiryu-san. <symbol=note_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "440||||4"
msgid "What does that even mean?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "441||||4"
msgid "Glad to hear it! <symbol=note_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "442||||4"
msgid "You say that to all the girls, don't you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "443||||4"
msgid "Oh gosh, I don't know what to say... <symbol=heart_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "444||||4"
msgid "Yahoo!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "445||||4"
msgid "You're like a cute little boy, Kiryu-san. <symbol=note_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "446||||4"
msgid "Hello to you too! Greetings are the\r\nfoundation of human interaction."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "447||||4"
msgid "What? No way! This isn't that kind of club!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "448||||4"
msgid "...You flatter me. <symbol=note_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "449||||4"
msgid "You probably say that to everyone, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "450||||4"
msgid "[Beautiful eyes...]"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "451||||4"
msgid "How nice... <symbol=heart_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "452||||4"
msgid "Whaaat? But looking at one person all\r\nthe time is pretty boring..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "453||||4"
msgid "Hmmmm... That's a secret. <symbol=note_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "454||||4"
msgid "Hmm, let me think... Yes. <symbol=note_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "455||||4"
msgid "Oh, is that so? Who?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "456||||4"
msgid "Hmm... I can't tell you... <symbol=heart_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "457||||4"
msgid "...I see."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "458||||4"
